[[div class="box" style="border:5px solid #5f009e; border-radius:5px; background-color:#100917; padding: 1em;"]]
[[div style="float:left; width: 240px; text-align: left; margin-top: 0; margin-left: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-right: 10px; padding-left: 10px;"]]
[[div style="color: #FFFFFF; font-size: 10pt; background-color:#321f4; font-family: "Microsoft Sans Serif"; border: #321f47 4px solid; background:#969696; text-align: left; padding: 2px 10px;"]]
Hi! :)
[[/div]]
[[div]]
[[image jaksmile.png width="130px" style="margin-left: 20px;"]]
[[/div]]
[[/div]]
[[div style="clear: left;"]]
[[/div]]

[[div style="float:right; width: 240px; text-align: right; margin-top: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 10px; padding-right: 10px;"]]
[[div style="color: #FFFFFF; font-size: 10pt; background-color:#321f4; font-family: "Microsoft Sans Serif"; border: #321f47 4px solid; background:#969696; text-align: left; padding: 2px 10px;"]]
Why hello indeed. Apologies for the rather... uncharacteristic appearance. It seems even gods are bound by [[[licensing-guide|your universe's rules]]], to some extent.
[[/div]]
[[div]]
[[image rallsmile.png width="130px" style="margin-right: 20px;"]]
[[/div]]
[[/div]]
[[div style="clear: right;"]]
[[/div]]

[[div style="float:left; width: 240px; text-align: left; margin-top: 0; margin-left: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-right: 10px; padding-left: 10px;"]]
[[div style="color: #FFFFFF; font-size: 10pt; background-color:#321f4; font-family: "Microsoft Sans Serif"; border: #321f47 4px solid; background:#969696; text-align: left; padding: 2px 10px;"]]
Make no mistake, though -- we're still who you think we are! Or, at least, we hope you know who we are?
[[/div]]
[[div]]
[[image jakhappy.png width="130px" style="margin-left: 20px;"]]
[[/div]]
[[/div]]
[[div style="clear: left;"]]
[[/div]]

[[div style="float:right; width: 240px; text-align: right; margin-top: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 10px; padding-right: 10px;"]]
[[div style="color: #FFFFFF; font-size: 10pt; background-color:#321f4; font-family: "Microsoft Sans Serif"; border: #321f47 4px solid; background:#969696; text-align: left; padding: 2px 10px;"]]
To clarify any possible confusion -- I'm still [[*user Ralliston]].
[[/div]]
[[div]]
[[image ralltalking.png width="130px" style="margin-right: 20px;"]]
[[/div]]
[[/div]]
[[div style="clear: right;"]]
[[/div]]

[[div style="float:left; width: 240px; text-align: left; margin-top: 0; margin-left: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-right: 10px; padding-left: 10px;"]]
[[div style="color: #FFFFFF; font-size: 10pt; background-color:#321f4; font-family: "Microsoft Sans Serif"; border: #321f47 4px solid; background:#969696; text-align: left; padding: 2px 10px;"]]
And I'm [[*user JakdragonX]]!
[[/div]]
[[div]]
[[image jakhappy.png width="130px" style="margin-left: 20px;"]]
[[/div]]
[[/div]]
[[div style="clear: left;"]]
[[/div]]

[[div style="float:right; width: 240px; text-align: right; margin-top: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 10px; padding-right: 10px;"]]
[[div style="color: #FFFFFF; font-size: 10pt; background-color:#321f4; font-family: "Microsoft Sans Serif"; border: #321f47 4px solid; background:#969696; text-align: left; padding: 2px 10px;"]]
Now, you might be thinking -- "what is this?"
[[/div]]
[[div]]
[[image rallsurprised.png width="130px" style="margin-right: 20px;"]]
[[/div]]
[[/div]]
[[div style="clear: right;"]]
[[/div]]

[[div style="float:left; width: 240px; text-align: left; margin-top: 0; margin-left: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-right: 10px; padding-left: 10px;"]]
[[div style="color: #FFFFFF; font-size: 10pt; background-color:#321f4; font-family: "Microsoft Sans Serif"; border: #321f47 4px solid; background:#969696; text-align: left; padding: 2px 10px;"]]
It's our shared authorpage hub, for all our collabs!
[[/div]]
[[div]]
[[image jakangry.png width="130px" style="margin-left: 20px;"]]
[[/div]]
[[/div]]
[[div style="clear: left;"]]
[[/div]]

[[div style="float:right; width: 240px; text-align: right; margin-top: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 10px; padding-right: 10px;"]]
[[div style="color: #FFFFFF; font-size: 10pt; background-color:#321f4; font-family: "Microsoft Sans Serif"; border: #321f47 4px solid; background:#969696; text-align: left; padding: 2px 10px;"]]
"But Jak and Ralliston," you say, "why did you make this page? Don't you have your [[[jakdragonx-rage-collection|own]]] [[[ralliston-s-authorpage|authorpages]]] already?"
[[/div]]
[[div]]
[[image rallglitch.png width="130px" style="margin-right: 20px;"]]
[[/div]]
[[/div]]
[[div style="clear: right;"]]
[[/div]]

[[div style="float:left; width: 240px; text-align: left; margin-top: 0; margin-left: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-right: 10px; padding-left: 10px;"]]
[[div style="color: #FFFFFF; font-size: 10pt; background-color:#321f4; font-family: "Microsoft Sans Serif"; border: #321f47 4px solid; background:#969696; text-align: left; padding: 2px 10px;"]]
We do! And we like them too. However, since we collab a lot -- like, a lot //a lot// -- we thought we'd try making something akin to a shared authorpage. There's no rules saying we can't have them, and you know what they say: "Science isn't about 'why?' It's about 'why not?!'"
[[/div]]
[[div]]
[[image jaksmile.png width="130px" style="margin-left: 20px;"]]
[[/div]]
[[/div]]
[[div style="clear: left;"]]
[[/div]]

[[div style="float:right; width: 240px; text-align: right; margin-top: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 10px; padding-right: 10px;"]]
[[div style="color: #FFFFFF; font-size: 10pt; background-color:#321f4; font-family: "Microsoft Sans Serif"; border: #321f47 4px solid; background:#969696; text-align: left; padding: 2px 10px;"]]
...did you just make a goddamned Portal 2 reference?
[[/div]]
[[div]]
[[image ralltalking.png width="130px" style="margin-right: 20px;"]]
[[/div]]
[[/div]]
[[div style="clear: right;"]]
[[/div]]

[[div style="float:left; width: 240px; text-align: left; margin-top: 0; margin-left: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-right: 10px; padding-left: 10px;"]]
[[div style="color: #FFFFFF; font-size: 10pt; background-color:#321f4; font-family: "Microsoft Sans Serif"; border: #321f47 4px solid; background:#969696; text-align: left; padding: 2px 10px;"]]
...perhaps.
[[/div]]
[[div]]
[[image jaksad.png width="130px" style="margin-left: 20px;"]]
[[/div]]
[[/div]]
[[div style="clear: left;"]]
[[/div]]

[[div style="float:right; width: 240px; text-align: right; margin-top: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 10px; padding-right: 10px;"]]
[[div style="color: #FFFFFF; font-size: 10pt; background-color:#321f4; font-family: "Microsoft Sans Serif"; border: #321f47 4px solid; background:#969696; text-align: left; padding: 2px 10px;"]]
Ignoring my friend's lack of social skills, I'd like to now officially welcome you to the appropriately titled "Ongoing Incident: JakdragonX & Ralliston," where we plan on showing you all the words we co-wrote together.
[[/div]]
[[div]]
[[image rallsmile.png width="130px" style="margin-right: 20px;"]]
[[/div]]
[[/div]]
[[div style="clear: right;"]]
[[/div]]

[[div style="float:left; width: 240px; text-align: left; margin-top: 0; margin-left: 0; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-right: 10px; padding-left: 10px;"]]
[[div style="color: #FFFFFF; font-size: 10pt; background-color:#321f4; font-family: "Microsoft Sans Serif"; border: #321f47 4px solid; background:#969696; text-align: left; padding: 2px 10px;"]]
Have fun!
[[/div]]
[[div]]
[[image jaksmile.png width="130px" style="margin-left: 20px;"]]
[[/div]]
[[/div]]
[[div style="clear: left;"]]
[[/div]]
[[/div]]
